## .NET / ASP.NET Core standard .gitignore

# Local secrets — never commit real connection strings/credentials
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.*.local.json
secrets.json

## Build results
bin/
obj/
out/

## User-specific files
*.user
*.userosscache
*.suo
*.userprefs

## Visual Studio
.vs/
*.VC.db
*.VC.VC.opendb

## Rider / JetBrains
.idea/
*.sln.iml

## VS Code
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json

## NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
**/[Pp]ackages/*
!**/[Pp]ackages/build/
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

## Rider/VS test & coverage
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
*.trx
coverage/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

## OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## Logs
*.log
logs/

## EF Core migrations bundle output (keep the Migrations folder itself, ignore generated bundles)
*.migrations.sql

## Publish output
publish/
PublishProfiles/*.pubxml.user

## Node (Playwright / local tooling)
node_modules/
